<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> counter_start [reuse, use_induction]:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∀ </span>#i x s<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
